},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"育美","body":"嗯，就算出去外面玩，\n有時也會因為很冷，沒辦法好好活動身體呢！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"2025birthdayStory-12-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薰","body":"是呀，我的生日正好落在\n那冬天的寒意正要告一段落的時候","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"2025birthdayStory-12-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薰","body":"我一直覺得，這應該有什麼深層的含意才對","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"2025birthdayStory-12-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"美咲","body":"欸，原來是這樣啊？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"2025birthdayStory-12-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薰","body":"如今，看到這份禮物我徹底明白了。\n原來我就是向冬天的寒意告別，\n為人們帶來溫暖微風的使者呀！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"smile04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"2025birthdayStory-12-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"心","body":"唉呀，原來是這樣！　真是美妙！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"2025birthdayStory-12-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"美咲","body":"說是溫暖的風，感覺氣溫好像已經很高了……\n呵呵，不過你這麼一說，感覺好像是耶","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"2025birthdayStory-12-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薰","body":"如此一來，無論冬天造訪幾次，\n人們都不會失去微笑","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"2025birthdayStory-12-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薰","bod